    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Tell Thunderbird Not to Wrap Lines When Sending Email]]></title>
    <link href="http://leetschau.github.io/blog/2013/10/31/104730/"/>
    <updated>2013-10-31T10:47:30+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://leetschau.github.io/blog/2013/10/31/104730</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>ThunderBird -> Edit -> Preferences -> Advanced -> General -> Config Editor:</p>

<p>Search &ldquo;wrap&rdquo;, change &ldquo;mail.wrap_long_lines&rdquo; to &ldquo;false&rdquo; and &ldquo;mailnews.wraplength&rdquo; to &ldquo;0&rdquo;.</p>

<p>Bingo!</p>
